{
  "texts": [
    "Automatic evaluation allows for faster evaluation by comparing MT outputs to human references.",
    "Some MT metrics include ChrF, which focuses on character n-grams rather than words to better handle morphologically rich languages.",
    "BLEU counts the matching n-grams between the MT and references.",
    "METEOR explicitly matches words and considers their recall and precision.",
    "It also matches the stems and synonyms."
  ]
}